@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vubppv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.01 - v2 + 0.61)) / wp.abs((v0 + 0.12 + v1 + 0.42)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.81 - v0 + 0.89)))
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.30 - v0 + 0.62) + (tmp + 0.29 * v1 + 0.57)))
    data[tid] = v0
